        <num>CHC 1309.3</num>
        <heading>1309.3.  Severability</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 1309.3.  Severability
If any provision of this Chapter or its application to any person or circumstance is
held invalid, the invalidity does not affect other provisions or applications of this Chapter
which can be given effect without the invalid provision or application, and to this end the
provisions of this Chapter are severable.</p>
        </content>
